Description_lang: Binds random players to both Silivaz and Pashmar. Upon expiration, Silivaz inflicts $297221s1 Physical damage to the player, while Pashmar inflicts $297223s1 Nature damage. Being close to either boss gains their favor, negating its damage.
AuraDescription_lang: Bound to both Might and Magic.Upon expiration, inflicts damage based on proximity to Silivaz and Pashmar.
